title: Osowo Małe, Gmina Lipnica
text:
Osowo Małe is a <a href="village">village</a> in the administrative district of <a href="Gmina%20Lipnica">Gmina Lipnica</a>, within <a href="Byt%C3%B3w%20County">Bytów County</a>, <a href="Pomeranian%20Voivodeship">Pomeranian Voivodeship</a>, in northern Poland. It lies approximately south-west of <a href="Lipnica%2C%20Pomeranian%20Voivodeship">Lipnica</a>, south-west of <a href="Byt%C3%B3w">Bytów</a>, and south-west of the regional capital <a href="Gda%C5%84sk">Gdańsk</a>.
For details of the history of the region, see "<a href="History%20of%20Pomerania">History of Pomerania</a>".
